definition.value: A secoiridoid glycoside that is [(2R,3E,4S)-3-ethylidene-2-hydroxy-5-(methoxycarbonyl)-3,4-dihydro-2H-pyran-4-yl]acetic acid in which the anometric hydroxy group has been converted to the corresponding beta-D-glucoside. It has been isolated from several plant species including Olea europaea.
